Running the App
Set Up React Native:

Install React Native CLI or Expo CLI for easier setup.
Initialize a new project:
bash
Copy code
npx expo init MechanicFinderApp
cd MechanicFinderApp
Install Dependencies:

bash
Copy code
npm install expo-location
Run the App:

For Android:
bash
Copy code
npx expo start --android
For iOS:
bash
Copy code
npx expo start --ios
